The recent introduction of Hollandia Evaporated Milk’s 120g pack size affectionately referred to as ”Pere” has been met with commendations from consumers. The new “Pere” pack is being seen as an irresistible way to deliver wholesome nutritious evaporated milk in a distinctive packaging. At a N100 price point, Hollandia Evap 120g ”Pere” pack has endeared itself to millions of consumers across Nigeria for its unique creamy taste and nourishing value in a convenient pack. It is tailored to fit specific consumer needs with quantity benefits and reasonably connects with an affordable price point. Among consumers who spoke was Mr. Oluseyi Adeniyi, a Brand Consultant with Marketing-Plus, who stated that while Hollandia Evap is already a household name in Nigeria for its product quality, affordability and satisfaction. Its new 120g “Pere” pack size is a packaging innovation that is making in-roads with its convenient portion size. The Company’s Managing Director, Mr. Roy Deepanjan, expressed delight on the feedback received so far from consumers.